❌ ❌ Hey everyone this is just a friendly reminder that unfortunately people make fake profiles using other peoples pictures. I’m not the only person this has happened to and if your not aware of the TV show called “Catfish” it’s literally a TV show about people using other peoples pictures off the internet to trick them. Please pay attention to who you respond to on the internet. I have 1 public Facebook page, 1 Instagram page (this one) and 1 TikTok page @ Nikitilley with 1 backup. With hundreds of thousands of fake profiles we can’t stop them all but you can simply report the fake page and move on. This has been happening for years unfortunately. ❌❌

I used to play the banjo, trumpet, drums, and guitar 3. My hair is naturally curly and I’ve never colored it in my life 4. You might have seen me on a few TV shows (CMT, Outdoor Channel, Sportsman Channel, Pursuit Channel, etc..) 5. Ive been in so many music videos I’ve lost count 6.
